        <h4 id="what-is-ai-slop-">What is AI Slop?</h4>
        <p><em>AI slop</em> is <strong>digital content</strong> made with <strong>generative artificial intelligence</strong> that is perceived as <em>lacking</em> in <strong>effort</strong>, <strong>quality</strong>, or <strong>meaning</strong>, and produced in <strong>high volume</strong> as <strong>clickbait</strong> to <em>gain advantage</em> in the attention economy, or earn <strong>money</strong>. It is a form of <strong>synthetic media</strong> usually linked to the monetization in the creator economy of social media and online advertising.</p>
