        <p>To spot AI, you must see how it is.</p>
        <br>
        <h5>Images:</h5>
        <p>Try to look for a yellow tint (reminesent of 2024 chatgpt ghibli craze), Deformations (Extra limbs, etc...) and images looking off.</p>
