        <p>Try to look for comments and broken parts. AI often overuses snippets it was trained on and often puts comments everywhere. Also look for border radius, glow, and other effects. AI often goes haywire over rounding, Dark colours, and glow on everything. AI generated code also often goes very haywire over variables.</p>
